### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@extraProductId = <pega_el_id_del_extra>

### ─────────────────────────────
### EXTRA PRODUCTS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear ensalada (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ensalada César",
  "category": "SALAD"
}

###

### Crear otra ensalada (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ensalada Completa",
  "category": "SALAD"
}

###

### Crear sándwich (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Sándwich de Pollo",
  "category": "SANDWICH"
}

###

### Crear otro sándwich (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Sándwich Jamón y Queso",
  "category": "SANDWICH"
}

###

### Listar todos los extras
GET {{baseUrl}}/extra-products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener extra por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/extra-products/{{extraProductId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar extra (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/extra-products/{{extraProductId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ensalada César Actualizada",
  "active": true
}

###

### Desactivar extra (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/extra-products/{{extraProductId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ensalada César",
  "active": false
}

###

### Eliminar extra (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/extra-products/{{extraProductId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
